extensionDescription.message: FileSystemBroker uses the Experiments API to provide limited access to the system file system. Its purpose is to make it so that other Web Extensions can write an read files without having to use the Experiments API directly. Access to the file system is limited to only a specific directory in the user's Profile Folder. It can write, read, check the existence, get file properties, get a list of files, etc
